## Outcome of this process

When you finish the pipeline, you will have: *one paragraph — ultimate deliverable(s), operator-green skill, or customer-facing artifact state.*

## High-level principles

- **Linear phases:** One row per **phase** in the master table below; **steps** stay inside each phase’s markdown under **`content/parts/phases/`**.
- **Normative contracts:** Cross-cutting rules live under **`content/parts/library/`**; the process table **Ref** column links to phase bodies, not duplicated prose.
- **Code vs AI:** **Code** runs scripts to exit codes and files; **AI / Human** follow phase instructions (see **`library/process-approach.md`** in **abd-skill-builder**).
- **Delivery:** Declare **`delivery.mode`** in **`skill-config.json`**; run **`python scripts/build.py`** after changing **`content/parts/`** when using **`static_built`**.

## Scripts and templates (this skill)

| Item | Role |
|------|------|
| **`scripts/build.py`** | Merges **`process.md`**, **`library/`**, phases, rules (per skill) into **`AGENTS.md`** and optional **`content/built/`**. |
| **`scripts/generate_prompt.py`** | Optional: emit AI-chat instruction blocks per phase (`--phase <slug>`, dynamic/static). |
| **`templates/`** (skill root) | Scaffold sources for **`scaffold_skill.py`** — not the same as **`content/parts/templates/`** here. |
| **`content/parts/templates/process-team.md.template`** (abd-skill-builder) | **Team process plate** to copy when authoring a rich **`process.md`**. |

